Employee count each Region.

Open new worksheet and drag and drop Region on column. 


Click Analysis then click Create Calculated Field. 


Calculated field name Taxes and Syntax - [Hourly Wage] *0.10 and then click OK. 



Drag and drop Taxes on the Row shelves and Level. 


Drag and drop Region on the color. 





Using the following link:

https://community.tableau.com/thread/253126
